{"tid":50013,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"阿仙奴轉會市場 : 確認簽入新蘇亞雷斯","createTime":"2016-12-22T06:20:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-08T10:33:41.000Z","uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d899f4e10f82267754d7a9adbf43b445bde71c48","tid":50013,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T06:20:09.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴增兵動作一向唔大，今夏只有兩簽。其中一簽係7月時由廣島三箭簽入日本國腳前鋒淺野拓磨，佢被視為日本最有前途的新星之一，更有「日本蘇亞雷斯」之稱。雲加大讚淺野非常有天份，睇嚟雲加都係一貫咁有耐性，唔想簽即食球員，而係繼續俾佢慢慢燉、慢慢炆。果然「如佢所願」，淺野申請工作證被拒，今季都係踢唔到，唯有安排外借，希望可以搵到德甲或者法甲球會俾佢落戶住先啦！21歲仔嘅淺野表示，收到兵工廠邀請嗰陣都O晒咀，坦言就算被外借，都會加盟兵工廠，似乎有晒心理準備。阿仙奴過去都簽過稻本潤一同宮市亮兩位日本球員，不過都未受雲加重用，睇吓淺野又有冇機會突破啦！"},{"pid":"7b067de2a2d42aca2304f23e925e1590d98a811b","tid":50013,"uid":11127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T06:21:12.000Z","msg":"睇漏左個新字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"007feed1cc8307a439d8469944d4e9651205854a","tid":50013,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T06:22:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e71c17a079424eebf8dddf6ce403dc43f18b17a4","tid":50013,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T06:24:20.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"0a3bcfb3d6035c78ebcf8efb02244a9c94610001","tid":50013,"uid":20224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T06:35:53.000Z","msg":"真命天子"},{"pid":"08eff8d967575aac2935027d028c5443d9c1a736","tid":50013,"uid":24063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T06:45:29.000Z","msg":"新蘇9 而家係邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48f594b0aa94cebe6b7c92d4a9401dc214425f56","tid":50013,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T06:49:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新蘇9 而家係邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /